dynGuiComponents.text:
Taking your medication properly is not easy, but now at least it won't be so difficult!
   
Please, take a look at what we have for you!

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: Keep all your drugs under control using the medication kit, and get easy access to package leaflets from official medicine databases.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text:
A routine is a time of the day at which you usually need to take some meds.

Do you take multiple medications at breakfast or lunch? Create a routine for that time, and Calendula will group all your intakes in a single notification.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: Create your medication agenda by using the schedules editor. You can link your intakes to your routines, define hourly or daily repetitions and much more!

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text:
Calendula will remind you about all your intakes. Remember to confirm, or we will notify you again!

Customize alarms in the settings menu.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text:
Calendula allows you to manage the medication of several patients, with their own medication kit, routines and schedules.

You will see all their intakes in the home screen.

AboutLibraries is a library to offer you all the information you need of your libraries! 

Most modern apps feature an Used Library-Section and for this some information of those libs is required. As it gets annoying to copy those strings always to your app I have developed this small helper library to provide the required information.
